{
  "texts": [
    "The specific knowledge acquisition tasks used in this approach are divided into three categories as below.",
    "The news article contents underwent additional processing using co-reference resolution and pronominal reference resolution [18], [20] with spaCy libraries.",
    "Next, the deep syntactic analysis steps illustrated in Fig. 2 are applied to extract essential information, such as entities, relationships between entities, and attributes.",
    "Attributes are properties associated with entities and relations.",
    "Based on the output, we identify the logical meaning of document sentences and extract logical form triads."
  ]
}